      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "<h2>Seckill Runtime Drilldown</h2><pre>inventory.seckill.requested\n  -> source consumer (read input)\n  -> FixedKeyProcessor\n  -> RocksDB inventory-store / dedupe-store\n  -> retry path: write back to inventory.seckill.requested\n  -> final path: write to inventory.seckill.result\n  -> changelog: dedupe/inventory store changelog topics</pre><p><strong>Metric mapping</strong></p><ul><li><code>input consumed/sec</code>: worker \u5f9e request topic \u5403\u9032\u4f86</li><li><code>retry writes/sec</code>: worker \u81ea\u5df1\u5beb\u56de request topic\uff0c\u4ee3\u8868 reroute/probe</li><li><code>result writes/sec</code>: final outcome \u5beb\u5230 result topic</li><li><code>changelog writes/sec</code>: RocksDB state \u8b8a\u66f4\u5beb\u56de changelog</li><li><code>partition lag</code>: request topic \u5404 partition \u5806\u7a4d</li><li><code>bytes by task/sink</code>: \u54ea\u4e9b task / sink topic \u6bd4\u8f03\u71b1</li></ul>",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.1.1",
      "title": "Topology and Reading Guide",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumer_consumer_fetch_manager_metrics_records_consumed_rate{topic=\"inventory.seckill.requested\"})",
          "legendFormat": "input consumed/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_producer_producer_topic_metrics_record_send_rate{topic=\"inventory.seckill.requested\"})",
          "legendFormat": "retry writes/sec",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_producer_producer_topic_metrics_record_send_rate{topic=\"inventory.seckill.result\"})",
          "legendFormat": "result writes/sec",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_producer_producer_topic_metrics_record_send_rate{topic=~\"minishop-seckill-worker-v2-.*-changelog\"})",
          "legendFormat": "changelog writes/sec",
          "refId": "D"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Request vs Retry vs Result vs Changelog",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
